Description:
Certain infectious and parasitic diseases. This category includes diseases caused by pathogenic microorganisms, such as bacteria, viruses, parasites, or fungi
.
subject: disease

Description: Neoplasms. This section covers all types of tumors, including benign, malignant, and those of uncertain behavior
subject: neoplasm

Description: Diseases of the blood and blood-forming organs and certain disorders involving the immune mechanism. This includes conditions like anemia and clotting disorders
subject: disorders

Description: Endocrine, nutritional, and metabolic diseases. This category encompasses disorders related to hormone imbalances, nutritional deficiencies, and metabolic dysfunctions
subject: disease

Description: Mental, Behavioral, and Neurodevelopmental disorders. This section includes mental health conditions such as depression, anxiety, and developmental disorders
subject: disorders

Description: Diseases of the nervous system. This includes conditions affecting the brain, spinal cord, and nerves, such as epilepsy and multiple sclerosis
subject: disease

Description: Diseases of the eye and adnexa. This category covers eye-related conditions, including cataracts and glaucoma
subject: disease

Description: Diseases of the ear and mastoid process. This includes hearing loss and infections of the ear
subject: disease

Description: Diseases of the circulatory system. This section includes heart diseases, hypertension, and vascular conditions
subject: disease

Description: Diseases of the respiratory system. This category covers conditions like asthma, pneumonia, and chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD)
subject: disease

Description: Diseases of the digestive system. This includes disorders of the stomach, intestines, liver, and pancreas
subject: disease

Description: Diseases of the skin and subcutaneous tissue. This section includes conditions like dermatitis and psoriasis
subject: disease

Description: Diseases of the musculoskeletal system and connective tissue. This category covers arthritis, osteoporosis, and related conditions
subject: disease

Description: Diseases of the genitourinary system. This includes kidney diseases, urinary tract infections, and reproductive system disorders
subject: disease

Description: Pregnancy, childbirth, and the puerperium. This section covers conditions related to pregnancy and childbirth
subject: pregnancy, childbirth

Description: Certain conditions originating in the perinatal period. This includes conditions affecting newborns
subject: conditions

Description: Congenital malformations, deformations, and chromosomal abnormalities. This category includes birth defects and genetic disorders
subject: birth defects/genetic disorders

Description: Symptoms, signs, and abnormal clinical and laboratory findings, not elsewhere classified. This section is for symptoms and signs that do not have a specific diagnosis
subject: symptoms, signs, findings

Description: Injury, poisoning, and certain other consequences of external causes. This includes injuries from accidents and poisonings
subject: injury/poisoning

Description: Codes for special purposes. This section is reserved for new diseases of uncertain etiology or other special purposes
subject: conditions

Description: External causes of morbidity. This includes codes for external causes of injuries and poisonings
subject: external causes

Description: Factors influencing health status and contact with health services. This category includes codes for factors that influence health status and encounters with health services
subject: factors
